						<h1 class="entry-title">A tenoning jig for the Dewalt DW745 portable table saw</h1>
								</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here&#8217;s a basic tenoning jig I made for my Dewalt DW745 portable table saw. It should make cutting tenons a breeze! (Click on the thumbnails below to see a larger version of each photo.)</p>
<p><a href="../blogfiles/20110319/IMG_3661.JPG" style="float:left;margin-right:10px;" class="lightbox"><img src="../blogfiles/20110319/thumbnails/IMG_3661.JPG" style="width:200px;height:150px;"></a></p>
